Name:           python-prettytable
Version:        3.2.0
Release:        2%{?dist}
License:        BSD
Vendor:         Microsoft Corporation
Distribution:   Azure Linux
Group:          Development/Languages/Python
URL:            https://github.com/jazzband/prettytable
